        <li><strong>Certification verification.</strong> We confirmed all claimed certifications (USDA Organic, Non-GMO Project, Vegan, Gluten-Free) against the respective certifying body databases.</li>
        <li><strong>Value calculation.</strong> Price per ounce was computed from the most common package size available on Amazon, factoring in Subscribe & Save discounts where available.</li>
